{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0101_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0101", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒", "中風"], "symptoms": [], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": ["下之"], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["小柴胡湯"], "treatment_principle": ["下之"], "alternatives": []}, "evidence_span": "傷寒中風，有柴胡證，但見一證便是，不必悉具。凡柴胡湯病證而下之，若柴胡證不罷者，復與柴胡湯，必蒸蒸而振，卻復發熱汗出而解。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為小柴胡湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「柴胡湯」，證據強度：給予（與）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "與", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.873, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0103_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0103", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["太陽病"], "symptoms": [], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": ["下之"], "time_course": ["四五日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["小柴胡湯"], "treatment_principle": ["下之"], "alternatives": ["大柴胡湯"]}, "evidence_span": "太陽病，過經十餘日，反二三下之。後四五日，柴胡證仍在者，先與小柴胡湯；嘔不止，心下急，鬱鬱微煩者，為未解也，與大柴胡湯下之則愈。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為小柴胡湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「小柴胡湯」，證據強度：給予（與）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "與", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.853, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0104_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0104", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒"], "symptoms": ["胸脅滿", "嘔", "日晡所發潮熱", "潮熱"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": ["下之"], "time_course": ["十三日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["小柴胡湯"], "treatment_principle": ["下之"], "alternatives": ["柴胡加芒消湯"]}, "evidence_span": "傷寒十三日不解，胸脅滿而嘔，日晡所發潮熱，已而微利。此本柴胡證，下之以不得利，今反利者，知醫以丸藥下之，此非其治也。潮熱者，實也。先宜服小柴胡湯以解外，後以柴胡加芒硝湯主之。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為小柴胡湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「小柴胡湯」，證據強度：建議用方（宜）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "宜", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.923, "release_level": "gold"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0123_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0123", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": [], "symptoms": ["欲嘔"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": [], "time_course": [], "contraindications": ["不可與"]}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["小柴胡湯"], "treatment_principle": [], "alternatives": ["調胃承氣湯", "調胃承氣湯"]}, "evidence_span": "太陽病，過經十餘日，心下溫溫欲吐，而胸中痛，大便反溏，腹微滿，鬱鬱微煩，先此時自極吐下者，與調胃承氣湯。若不爾者，不可與。但欲嘔，胸中痛，微溏者，此非柴胡湯證，以嘔，故知極吐下也。調胃承氣湯。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為小柴胡湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「柴胡湯」，證據強度：證屬（屬）。本條同時載明禁忌「不可與」，用方須以該禁忌為前提。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "屬", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": ["repair:contraindication_annotated:不可與"], "consensus_score": 0.883, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0144_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0144", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["中風", "熱入血室"], "symptoms": ["如瘧狀"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": [], "time_course": ["七八日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["小柴胡湯"], "treatment_principle": [], "alternatives": []}, "evidence_span": "婦人中風，七八日續得寒熱，發作有時，經水適斷者，此為熱入血室，其血必結，故使如瘧狀，發作有時，小柴胡湯主之。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為小柴胡湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「小柴胡湯主之」，證據強度：主治關係（主之）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.9, "prescription_strength": "主之", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.956, "release_level": "gold"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0148_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0148", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒", "少陰病"], "symptoms": ["頭汗出", "微惡寒", "大便硬", "汗出"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": ["細", "沉", "沉緊"], "prior_treatment": [], "time_course": ["五六日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["小柴胡湯"], "treatment_principle": [], "alternatives": []}, "evidence_span": "傷寒五六日，頭汗出，微惡寒，手足冷，心下滿，口不欲食，大便硬，脈細者，此為陽微結，必有表，復有裏也。脈沉，亦在裏也。汗出，為陽微。假令純陰結，不得復有外證，悉入在裏，此為半在裏半在外也。脈雖沉緊，不得為少陰病。所以然者，陰不得有汗，今頭汗出，故知非少陰也。可與小柴胡湯，設不了了者，得屎而解。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為小柴胡湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「小柴胡湯」，證據強度：斟酌可用（可與）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "可與", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "warn", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.833, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0149_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0149", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒"], "symptoms": ["嘔", "發熱"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": [], "time_course": ["五六日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["小柴胡湯"], "treatment_principle": ["下之"], "alternatives": ["大陷胸湯", "半夏瀉心湯"]}, "evidence_span": "傷寒五六日，嘔而發熱者，柴胡湯證具，而以他藥下之，柴胡證仍在者，復與柴胡湯。此雖已下之，不為逆，必蒸蒸而振，卻發熱汗出而解。若心下滿而硬痛者，此為結胸也，大陷胸湯主之。但滿而不痛者，此為痞，柴胡不中與之，宜半夏瀉心湯。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為小柴胡湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「柴胡湯」，證據強度：證屬（屬）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "屬", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.923, "release_level": "gold"}}
